but also to the fear of losing.

68
00:06:07,859 --> 00:06:09,668
So,

69
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,140
is it because you care about me?

70
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:22,560
Don't worry. I always remember it.

71
00:06:23,499 --> 00:06:26,040
Now, I'm not just fighting for myself.

72
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:29,364
I still have you.

73
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,239
Yesterday, I asked a friend.

74
00:06:35,239 --> 00:06:37,439
The driver was only slightly injured yesterday.

75
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:40,100
After receiving treatment, he has woken up.

76
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:45,820
If you don't believe me, I can show you my chatting records.

77
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,580
No need. I believe you.

78
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:54,904
See you tomorrow.

79
00:07:10,624 --> 00:07:12,680
[Zhao Yingning]

80
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,904
Let's meet and chat.

81
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:23,299
Don't worry. It's about work.

82
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,600
What's the matter?

83
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:37,279
Hello, do you need something to drink?

84
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:39,700
- No need. Just get me another cup please. 
- Alright

85
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:41,228
Thank you.

86
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:48,839
How are you and Chen Mobai doing recently?

87
00:07:50,359 --> 00:07:55,479
Miss Zhao, you said you wanted to talk about work.

88
00:07:55,479 --> 00:07:58,819
Okay. Let's talk about work.

89
00:07:58,819 --> 00:08:01,340
What did you think of today's test?

90
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:07,152
Test? Normal, I guess.

91
00:08:07,152 --> 00:08:08,792
Normal?

92
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:11,820
I think you are the one
who said you wanted to talk about work,

93
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:14,320
but it seems like
you want to talk about feelings now.

94
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,420
Let me cut to the chase.

95
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:24,579
I think your relationship with Chen Mobai

96
00:08:24,579 --> 00:08:26,940
has already affected the race.

97
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:29,380
It doesn't matter
if it's Chen Mobai or Ruifeng,

98
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:33,280
what they need now isn't just a normal score.

99
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,340
They need perfection.

100
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:38,179
They need a certain victory.

101
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:41,939
That was also the promise he made
in order to be with you at the time.

102
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:51,064
He will do it. And I will do it too.

103
00:08:51,064 --> 00:08:54,099
No matter what our relationship is,

104
00:08:54,099 --> 00:08:56,900
it will not affect the racing.

105
00:08:56,900 --> 00:09:01,419
May I ask what makes you so confident?

106
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,659
This is a cross-section of the brain.

107
00:09:16,659 --> 00:09:19,740
This is the primary motor cortex
of the central anterior gyrus in the brain,

108
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:21,759
which is responsible for controlling movement.

109
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:23,920
Here is the anterior cingulate cortex,

110
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:26,059
which is responsible for controlling emotions.

111
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:30,900
The emotional issues you worry about will not affect Chen Mobai

112
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:34,419
because these two areas do not overlap.

113
00:09:34,419 --> 00:09:35,756
Okay.

114
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:39,052
It won't affect Chen Mobai.

115
00:09:39,052 --> 00:09:41,192
What about you then?

116
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:50,840
I will try to use your way to communicate my thoughts with you.

117
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,719
I don't know whether you have heard of
something called paradox.

118
00:09:54,719 --> 00:09:57,560
The paradox of emotion and reason.

119
00:09:57,560 --> 00:10:02,300
Formula racing is originally the fastest sport on earth.

120
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:05,719
Its safety and speed are
inherently contradictory.

121
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:07,900
Just like the relationship
between racers and engineers

122
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:10,720
should be purely contractual.

123
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,860
They should learn about each other

124
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:15,979
and maintain a dangerous contradiction.

125
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:27,760
But if there is something uncontrollable in between,

126
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,840
which disrupts this balance,

127
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:31,919
what do you think will happen?

128
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:36,060
It's just like the special worry

129
00:10:37,019 --> 00:10:39,116
you and Chen Mobai have now.

130
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:47,619
Wanting too much will lose balance.

131
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:52,359
Now it has lost its practicality
for holding wine,

132
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,900
and also affects the aesthetics of the glass.

133
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:57,339
At the same time,
it wasted a great bottle of wine.

134
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,339
I know what you want to say.

135
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:12,720
I'm still adjusting the data.

136
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,179
I'm still searching.

137
00:11:14,179 --> 00:11:17,299
I will find the most suitable tuning
for Chen Mobai.

138
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:20,328
You're just scared.

139
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:28,700
As an engineer, I've lost some very important people.

140
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:31,580
What I can do now is at least not to let anyone

141
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:33,980
have an accident in the car I designed.

142
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,140
But the one you are most afraid of losing

143
00:11:36,140 --> 00:11:38,979
is him, isn't it?

144
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:47,040
You see, human emotions are the most complex things in the world.

145
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:50,920
They can't be controlled, and there's no way to measure them.

146
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:53,060
Chen Mobai is the same.

147
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:56,200
I've known him for over a decade,

148
00:11:56,200 --> 00:12:00,040
and he had never said the word 'tired',

149
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:04,360
but today, for you, he took all the responsibility.

150
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,779
The paradox is mutual.

151
00:12:07,779 --> 00:12:09,996
He cares about you,

152
00:12:09,996 --> 00:12:12,759
so he doesn't want to make you worry.

153
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:16,056
You also care about him, so you can't let go.

154
00:12:16,056 --> 00:12:18,659
You can't let him run as fast as he can.

155
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:24,500
Even if this paradox is true,

156
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:28,460
I believe that as long as there's a problem, there must be an answer.

157
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:36,679
Actually, I'm not here today to question you

158
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:42,728
as an investor or to suppress you as a competitor?

159
00:12:42,728 --> 00:12:47,440
You can consider me as a friend of both of you.

160
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:51,679
I hope you think carefully about your current situation.

161
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:55,220
Chen Mobai is now shouldering, not just his own dreams,

162
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:57,220
but also Ruifeng.

163
00:12:58,679 --> 00:13:01,600
Ruifeng was founded by his parents.

164
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:04,840
It has extraordinary meaning
to the Chen siblings.

165
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:07,999
So he must push forward, and he can only push forward.

166
00:13:07,999 --> 00:13:10,840
Of course,
I know you have your own considerations,

167
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:16,919
but as a friend, I suggest you consider all possibilities.

168
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:27,519
If there's nothing else, I'll leave now.

169
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:32,479
I hope it's really as you said.

170
00:13:35,919 --> 00:13:38,024
Wish you good luck.

171
