174
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:23,708
Why did Shen Xi change the data during the day?

175
00:14:26,159 --> 00:14:27,868
Is it because she got scared

176
00:14:27,868 --> 00:14:31,039
after seeing the news from the past few days?

177
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,380
I have received definite information.

178
00:14:38,380 --> 00:14:44,019
Mitsui Taku and Lu Yunhao also ran the Linhai track this afternoon.

179
00:14:44,019 --> 00:14:48,680
And both of their latest lap times surpassed the record you just broke.

180
00:14:49,639 --> 00:14:52,052
And it's considerably exceeded.

181
00:14:52,052 --> 00:14:54,380
Impossible.

182
00:14:54,380 --> 00:14:57,259
Are they playing some kind of
psychological tactic?

183
00:14:57,259 --> 00:15:00,468
It's not psychological tactics. It's actual strength.

184
00:15:00,468 --> 00:15:03,940
I heard they always wanted to invite an expert from Europe,

185
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:07,680
and this expert has agreed to teach them recently.

186
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:09,159
It's only been a few days,

187
00:15:09,159 --> 00:15:11,500
and this kind of result has been achieved.

188
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:18,839
I am just giving you a heads up.

189
00:15:18,839 --> 00:15:20,812
Don't think too much.

190
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:28,304
Don't worry. Strong enemies make you stronger.

191
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,352
It actually motivates us more.

192
00:15:32,352 --> 00:15:34,336
Go to sleep

193
00:15:48,759 --> 00:15:52,540
I can definitely debug the perfect data.

