00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:14,948
Any objections?

197
00:16:14,948 --> 00:16:17,519
Why is it only us attending
such an important meeting?

198
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,520
Where is Xi?

199
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:21,544
She went back to adjust the data.

200
00:16:22,799 --> 00:16:25,259
Wait. You guys, what's happening?

201
00:16:25,259 --> 00:16:27,879
Backing off before the competition?

202
00:16:29,159 --> 00:16:31,220
Is it because you heard
they increased their speed?

203
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:33,984
- Did that scare you? 
 - We are not scared.

204
00:16:33,984 --> 00:16:37,160
We just feel that the difficulty of the competition has increased

205
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,920
which means it is even more difficult
to win the championship.

206
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:43,900
As the saying goes, full steam ahead initially,

207
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:46,440
decreased afterwards, exhausted at the end.

208
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,300
If you think I might be overwhelmed,

209
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:51,799
I can ensure you all that I won't be.

210
00:16:51,799 --> 00:16:56,100
On the battlefield, to become the strongest,

211
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:58,959
one must defeat those stronger.

212
00:16:58,959 --> 00:17:02,240
Okay. Ningwan Station.

213
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:04,940
First battle victory. Come on.

214
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:07,640
Skyfall!

215
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,419
Well done, Mobai. You did great today.

216
00:17:17,419 --> 00:17:19,939
In our first Formula A race,
we got second place.

217
00:17:19,939 --> 00:17:22,599
