220
00:17:34,799 --> 00:17:35,840
Push it in.

221
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,944
Is it fun?

222
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,776
What?

223
00:18:08,279 --> 00:18:09,376
Wind.

224
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,088
Do you feel it?

225
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:21,632
I feel it.

226
00:18:24,559 --> 00:18:25,839
Your hands are chilled by the wind.

227
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,480
Miss Shen, we are from Daily Sports.

228
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,528
we want to know that after two years,

229
00:18:30,528 --> 00:18:31,580
how do you feel returning to the track?

230
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:32,880
We're from Weekly Magazine. Do you--

231
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,340
Excuse me. The race will start soon.

232
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:36,720
If you want an interview,

233
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,299
it will be arranged
by the organizing committee after the race.

234
00:18:38,299 --> 00:18:39,560
Could you please answer me?

235
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:40,700
Could you please say something?

236
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:41,839
We have an exclusive interview.

237
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:45,300
Why are there suddenly so many media?

238
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:47,559
It's okay. There's nothing to fear. We're here.

239
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,480
Chen Mobai.

240
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,720
Are you busy dating?

241
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:57,400
People talk about having it all.
Both love and career.

242
00:18:57,960 --> 00:19:00,680
Why do I feel that Mobai's career is
not going smoothly,

243
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:03,200
so he can only focus on love?

244
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:09,680
Why do I smell jealousy?

245
00:19:10,279 --> 00:19:11,880
Do you mean I'm jealous of you? About what?

246
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,959
Jealous that your test-driving record
was broken by me.

247
00:19:14,959 --> 00:19:16,680
You are jealous of my good mentality, right?

248
00:19:17,519 --> 00:19:19,600
Unlike some people. After losing their ranking,

249
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,280
they quickly come to blabber.

250
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:22,799
Chen Mobai, what are you talking about?

251
00:19:23,559 --> 00:19:24,672
Who is this?

252
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:28,000
Isn't this the manager of the Satellite team?

253
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:31,260
You're relying on
Takano's technology and coaching.

254
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:32,559
You'd better stay low-key.

255
00:19:32,559 --> 00:19:33,880
Chen Mobai, don't be so arrogant.

256
00:19:34,599 --> 00:19:37,359
Isn't she just a Super Grand Prix engineer?

257
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,960
If you lose this time,

258
00:19:39,519 --> 00:19:40,780
you will not only embarrass yourself

259
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:41,840
but also others.

260
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:44,799
Good racers speak through their engines.

